1. Clone the project.
2. Create a symlink in the "~/Library/Application Support/FDT/projectTypes" folder to the rss.xml file:

	ln -s ./rss.xml ~/Library/Application\ Support/FDT/projectTypes/rss.xml
	
3. Create a symlink in the "~/Library/Application Support/FDT/projectTemplates/Web/" folder to the RocketScienceStudiosAS3 folder:

	ln -s ./RocketScienceStudiosAS3 ~/Library/Application\ Support/FDT/projectTemplates/Web/RocketScienceStudiosAS3
	
4. (Re)start FDT and create a new project with these settings: http://grabs.epologee.com/db3359b77175a31adfd030570d99793f.png
5. Add custom linked libraries
6. Run the *App.as as an FDT AS3 Application
7. Done!